Purpose… purpose is not always black and white, sometimes it’s scary, sometimes it’s exciting and fulfilling. Our biggest mistake in life is thinking that ‘Purpose’ needs to look a certain way, and that ‘Purpose’ is the ‘big’ final destination, a place you arrive at… meanwhile purpose is the small intentional steps that you take in between each day, it’s the culmination of the small ‘ahah’ moments, it’s the process. It’s the wins, it’s the failures, it’s the lessons. Purpose is being intentional with the small blessings that God grants you each day.

God, thank You for trusting me with so much at such a young age. I sometimes still feel like my dreams are too big, but I quickly remind myself that I serve an even bigger God. 

To you, my community, my ‘Purpose’ in life is nothing without your support. I’ll forever be grateful for the opportunity to serve and impact you. ❤️

(Last Frame) A little girl can only dream… but oh I serve a God of miracles.
God is the Artist, I’m just His canvas. ♥️
